Package: scAFAP
Type: Package
Title: Adaptive Fragment-based Alternative Polyadenylation Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Min Su
Maintainer: Min Su <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: 
    A framework for adaptive fragment-based analysis of alternative polyadenylation (APA) from single-cell RNA-seq data. 
    It identifies and quantifies APA isoforms by leveraging fragment size and polyA reads.
